'''环己硫醇'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>11</sub>SH，它是具有强烈气味的无色液体。

==制备==
环己硫醇最初由环己烷和二硫化碳的反应制得。<ref name=chicago>{{cite journal |last=Kharasch |first=M.S. |last2=Eberly |first2=Kenneth |date=February 1941 |title=Reactions of Atoms and Free Radicals in Solution. III. The Introduction of a Mercaptan Group into Cyclohexane |journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc. |volume=63 |issue=2 |pages=625 |doi=10.1021/ja01847a508 }}</ref>它在工业上由[[环己酮|环己酮]]在[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]的存在下（金属硫化物作为催化剂）氢化得到：
:C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>10</sub>O  +  H<sub>2</sub>S  +  H<sub>2</sub>   →   C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>11</sub>SH  +  H<sub>2</sub>O
它也可有[[环己烯|环己烯]]和[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]在[[硫化镍|硫化镍]]的存在下经加成反应制得。<ref name=Ullmann>Kathrin-Maria Roy "Thiols and Organic sulphides" in ''Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry'', 2002, Wiley-VCH Verlag, Weinheim. {{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a26_767}}</ref>

